channel.title: A Mopar Clan?
channel.description:
I know this has been done before, and no one really cared about it. So tell me to stfu if you want, but how would you guys feel about me setting up a Mopar clan? Not one of those ones made half assed, but a proper one.
I have my domain which is simple going to waste right now, so maybe we could set it up there or, even better, if it works out that is, get a clan board on this forum.
Before even thinking about that, I need opinions on me setting up a clan for all of us, no matter what level, with PKing trips, CW trips, the whole deal.

item.description:

[quote=“PaulT, post:55, topic:117397”]Eh, whatever. Don’t promote that shit, man, just by posting the link you vindicate his stupidity.

Anyway, if you think I have a point with the TC mod for Runescape idea maybe you would want to do someshit with that. e.g. Make one.

I’m not really sure what people are interested in, anyway. A dungeons and dragons style quest with lots of skill use (and taking 1/20 on chances) might be a lot of fun to make even if nobody plays it and probably easy to make as well given all the formulas you need for shit are in the books (PDF from limewire if you are poor to buy lel) and the game is turn based. On the multiplayer front I don’t really know, maybe Runescape on drugs or something might be fun just visually or really any kind of graphical TC mod would be pretty awesome at this point.

It’s been along time since WL released the first RS2 server man, years, somebody should make something good. Oh wait, that’s me…Just too fucking lazy, and now I’m busy with other shit. I wish I’d done this more last year when I actually I had time. Oh well.[/quote]
